<h2 style="font-size: 22px;">Mississippi Gulf Coast Community College</h2>
<strong>Perkinston, MS</strong>

<div class="infolines">
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers credit for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-green">Yes</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
    <div class="row-fluid">
        <div class="span10">Offers placement into higher-level courses for AP Exams</div>
        <div class="span2 alignRight">
                <div class="short-status-red">No</div>
        </div>
    </div>    
</div>


<p>
    <strong>From the college:</strong>
    <i>Students entering MGCCC will be allowed credit on the Advanced Placement Examination administered by the College Board and sponsored by participating high schools. For an Advanced Placement score of 4 or 5, 6 or 8 semester hours will be awarded if offered by the college in that subject area. For scores of 3, 3 or 4 semester hours will be awarded if MGCCC college credit is offered in the specific subject areas that the AP credit was earned.</i>
    <br/>
    For more information, <a href="http://www.mgccc.edu/future_students/college_catalogs.php" target="_blank" title="Opens a new window">view the credit policy on this college's website</a>.
</p>

